            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ is coming as a King to spread His kingdom on earth."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He will reign with all His saints who know His kingdom’s worth."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Reign in all my life, dear King; I give You full permission."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Under Your authority, I’m given Your dominion."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ will come still as a Man—the Son of Man forever."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "First He was God’s only Son, now He has many brothers."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Father’s Firstborn Son now has a pure duplication;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We truly match each other—we are divine and human."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
